channel.description:
[b]This tut is about how to make a Godwars killcount on right corner of your client screen.[/b]

[b]Used files[/b] Class9.java, texture.java , client.java.

Open up your class9 in your client folder.

Add this first in class9 if you don't have it:
[code]public static void addText(int id, String text, Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4 wid[], int idx, int color) {
		Class9 Tab = addTab(id);
		Tab.anInt250 = id;
		Tab.anInt236 = id;
		Tab.anInt262 = 4;
		Tab.anInt217 = 0;
		Tab.anInt220 = 174;
		Tab.anInt267 = 11;
		Tab.anInt214 = 0;
		Tab.aByte254 = 0;
		Tab.anInt230 = -1;
		Tab.aBoolean223 = false;
		Tab.aBoolean268 = true;
		Tab.aClass30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4_243 = wid[idx];
		Tab.aString248 = text;
		Tab.aString228 = "";
		Tab.anInt232 = color;
		Tab.anInt219 = 0;
		Tab.anInt216 = 0;
		Tab.anInt239 = 0;	
	}[/code]

Add this method in it.
Search for "public static void" and add it somewhere after a bracket.

[code]	public static void GodWars(Class30_Sub2_Sub1_Sub4[] wid)
{
Class9 Tab = addTab(16210);
addText(16211, "NPC killcount", wid, 1, 0xff9040);
addText(16212, "Armadyl kills", wid, 1, 0xff9040);
addText(16213, "Bandos kills", wid, 1, 0xff9040);
addText(16214, "Saradomin kills", wid, 1, 0xff9040);
addText(16215, "Zamorak kills", wid, 1, 0xff9040);
addText(16216, "0", wid, 1, 0x66FFFF);//armadyl
addText(16217, "0", wid, 1, 0x66FFFF);//bandos
addText(16218, "0", wid, 1, 0x66FFFF);//saradomin
addText(16219, "0", wid, 1, 0x66FFFF);//zamorak
Tab.aBoolean266 = false;
Tab.anIntArray240 = new int[9];
Tab.anIntArray241 = new int[9];
Tab.anIntArray272 = new int[9];
Tab.anIntArray240[0] = 16211;
Tab.anIntArray241[0] = -52+375;
Tab.anIntArray272[0] = 7;
Tab.anIntArray240[1] = 16212;
Tab.anIntArray241[1] = -52+374;
Tab.anIntArray272[1] = 30;
Tab.anIntArray240[2] = 16213;
Tab.anIntArray241[2] = -52+372;
Tab.anIntArray272[2] = 44;
Tab.anIntArray240[3] = 16214;
Tab.anIntArray241[3] = -52+381;
Tab.anIntArray272[3] = 58;
Tab.anIntArray240[4] = 16215;
Tab.anIntArray241[4] = -52+375;
Tab.anIntArray272[4] = 73;
Tab.anIntArray240[5] = 16216;
Tab.anIntArray241[5] = -52+455;
Tab.anIntArray272[5] = 31;
Tab.anIntArray240[6] = 16217;
Tab.anIntArray241[6] = -52+455;
Tab.anIntArray272[6] = 45;
Tab.anIntArray240[7] = 16218;
Tab.anIntArray241[7] = -52+455;
Tab.anIntArray272[7] = 59;
Tab.anIntArray240[8] = 16219;
Tab.anIntArray241[8] = -52+455;
Tab.anIntArray272[8] = 74;
}[/code]

After search for:
[code]aclass44 = class44[/code]
or 
[code]aclass44 = aclass44[/code]

under it add:
[code]GodWars(aclass30_sub2_sub1_sub4);[/code]

__________________________________________________

Server sided:

Search for:
[code]public class client extends Player implements Runnable {[/code]

Under it add:
[code]public int ArmadylkillCount = 0;
public int BandoskillCount = 0;
public int SarakillCount = 0;
public int ZammykillCount = 0;[/code]

If you wan't it to use like an interface, us this:
[code]setInterfaceWalkable(16210);[/code]

Open up texthandler in your server folder and add this in it:
[code]c.sendQuest("                          0", 16216);
c.sendQuest("                          0", 16217);
c.sendQuest("                          0", 16218);
c.sendQuest("                          0", 16219);
c.sendQuest("                  NPC killcount", 16211);
c.sendQuest("                  Armadyl kills:", 16212);
c.sendQuest("                   Bandos kills:", 16213);
c.sendQuest("                Saradomin kills:", 16214);
c.sendQuest("                  Zamorak kills:", 16215);[/code]

You're done!
Post any errors here!

